00:10:14,154 --> 00:10:19,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter what, I want to have
seen the end of this game by then.</b></font>

149
00:10:19,114 --> 00:10:22,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To get straight to the point...
I desire your technique!</b></font>

150
00:10:24,514 --> 00:10:27,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Won't you join our team,
and participate as a driver?</b></font>

151
00:10:27,794 --> 00:10:29,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>M-Me?!</b></font>

152
00:10:29,754 --> 00:10:33,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You are the man who put
an end to my winning record.</b></font>

153
00:10:33,834 --> 00:10:37,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course, because this is
my game, should you participate,</b></font>

154
00:10:37,834 --> 00:10:40,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I believe I can reward you as is appropriate.</b></font>

155
00:10:40,474 --> 00:10:42,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Reward"?</b></font>

156
00:10:42,234 --> 00:10:47,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You have made it this far racing
on talent and sense alone.</b></font>

157
00:10:47,034 --> 00:10:51,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But soon, you should find
yourself coming up against a wall.</b></font>

158
00:10:51,874 --> 00:10:55,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Clearing that wall, heading toward
the area that lies farther beyond,</b></font>

159
00:10:55,674 --> 00:10:59,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>will require driving supported
by precise theoretical concepts.</b></font>

160
00:10:59,114 --> 00:11:02,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In order to get faster,
you will require knowledge.</b></font>

161
00:11:02,354 --> 00:11:06,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Have you not begun to notice this yourself?</b></font>

162
00:11:06,234 --> 00:11:08,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can understand...</b></font>

163
00:11:08,474 --> 00:11:13,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...because you are a type of
driver much like my brother.</b></font>

164
00:11:13,394 --> 00:11:15,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like Keisuke?</b></font>

165
00:11:15,354 --> 00:11:19,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To couple instinctive talent
with theory is to be unstoppable.</b></font>

166
00:11:19,234 --> 00:11:23,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I will teach you that which you most require.</b></font>

167
00:11:23,474 --> 00:11:28,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And it is best learned while
experiencing racers' local courses.</b></font>

168
00:11:29,674 --> 00:11:31,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do this with us.</b></font>

169
00:11:31,714 --> 00:11:35,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't have to answer now. Think it over.</b></font>

170
00:11:35,034 --> 00:11:36,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>O-Okay.</b></font>

171
00:11:45,194 --> 00:11:47,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I await a favorable response.</b></font>

172
00:11:59,394 --> 00:12:04,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You were invited into some new team
Ryosuke Takahashi's making?!</b></font>

173
00:12:04,754 --> 00:12:09,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He says it'll be active for just
one year before disbanding...</b></font>

174
00:12:09,034 --> 00:12:11,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Some kind of special team that'll
be going outside our prefecture.</b></font>

175
00:12:11,954 --> 00:12:16,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Th-Th-That's awesome!
It's <i>super</i> crazy big news!</b></font>

176
00:12:16,994 --> 00:12:19,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wanna hurry up and tell lketani!!</b></font>

177
00:12:19,634 --> 00:12:23,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Look, please don't turn this
into some big deal, all right?</b></font>

178
00:12:23,034 --> 00:12:25,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm still not close to deciding.</b></font>

179
00:12:27,314 --> 00:12:31,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's there to decide?!</b></font>

180
00:12:31,274 --> 00:12:35,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I mean, my first race was this past summer...</b></font>

181
00:12:35,394 --> 00:12:37,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It hasn't even been six months yet.</b></font>

182
00:12:37,914 --> 00:12:41,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's only recently I've even
become interested in cars...</b></font>

183
00:12:41,474 --> 00:12:45,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm nervous whether someone like me
could make it as a team member.</b></font>

184
00:12:45,994 --> 00:12:48,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you talking about?
Since your first year in middle school,</b></font>

185
00:12:48,634 --> 00:12:50,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you've raced the mountain pass
delivering tofu, right?!</b></font>

186
00:12:50,994 --> 00:12:52,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll be fine!</b></font>

187
00:12:52,674 --> 00:12:56,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Aargh! I'll do odd jobs or anything,
just let me in, too!</b></font>

188
00:12:56,634 --> 00:12:59,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is awesome! It's too awesome!!</b></font>

189
00:12:59,954 --> 00:13:03,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey! All you rivals of mine!</b></font>

190
00:13:03,314 --> 00:13:06,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>More and more, you'll be left in the dust!</b></font>

191
00:13:06,954 --> 00:13:10,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, I've been all mixed up
over this since yesterday.</b></font>

192
00:13:10,514 --> 00:13:12,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel like before I join that team,</b></font>

193
00:13:12,154 --> 00:13:16,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>there are a couple of things
that I'm going to have to do...</b></font>

194
00:13:20,994 --> 00:13:25,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Incredible! That's what
Ryosuke Takahashi had to say?</b></font>

195
00:13:25,474 --> 00:13:29,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right?! That's some
super-awesome big news, huh?</b></font>

196
00:13:29,034 --> 00:13:33,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah! Ryosuke Takahashi represents
the charisma of us street drivers...</b></font>

197
00:13:33,954 --> 00:13:37,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The king of the mountain pass,
winning battle after battle!</b></font>

198
00:13:37,874 --> 00:13:42,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was Takumi who put a stop to
that record of consecutive wins,</b></font>

199
00:13:42,114 --> 00:13:47,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so if the two of them paired up,
it would make a powerful team, but...</b></font>

200
00:13:47,954 --> 00:13:51,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have mixed feelings about this.</b></font>

201
00:13:53,074 --> 00:13:56,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi is the hero of our Akina Speed Stars.</b></font>

202
00:13:56,674 --> 00:14:00,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you feel like that's
being taken by the Red Suns?</b></font>

203
00:14:00,794 --> 00:14:05,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think that Takumi should spend
more and more time out there.</b></font>

204
00:14:05,034 --> 00:14:09,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want him to grow, really improve himself.</b></font>

205
00:14:09,314 --> 00:14:14,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just think of him being "on loan"
to Ryosuke Takahashi for a year.</b></font>

206
00:14:14,674 --> 00:14:16,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An expedition outside our prefecture, eh?</b></font>

207
00:14:16,714 --> 00:14:20,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Long ago, we considered that as well.</b></font>

208
00:14:20,194 --> 00:14:21,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He should go.</b></font>

209
00:14:21,554 --> 00:14:25,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi isn't the type to be
content with just the Akina pass.</b></font>

210
00:14:39,954 --> 00:14:42,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A blown engine means defeat.</b></font>

211
00:15:24,434 --> 00:15:26,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello?</b></font>

212
00:15:26,754 --> 00:15:28,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is he.</b></font>

213
00:15:28,314 --> 00:15:33,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um, sorry. This doesn't have to do
with our talk yesterday, but...</b></font>

214
00:15:33,234 --> 00:15:36,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, maybe it's not <i>completely</i> unrelated.</b></font>

215
00:15:36,914 --> 00:15:40,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's something I'd like you to tell me...</b></font>

216
00:15:40,634 --> 00:15:45,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The leader of Team Emperor?
You mean Kyoichi Sudou?</b></font>

217
00:15:45,674 --> 00:15:51,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. Do you know where I could
go to meet this "Sudou" person?</b></font>

218
00:15:51,274 --> 00:15:54,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kyoichi is an old acquaintance of mine.</b></font>

219
00:15:54,074 --> 00:15:57,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I could get hold of him
at any time, if I so wished...</b></font>

220
00:15:57,634 --> 00:15:59,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I...</b></font>

221
00:15:59,594 --> 00:16:04,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought that if I had the chance,
I'd like to race him again.</b></font>

222
00:16:04,354 --> 00:16:07,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. And where do you intend to do this?</b></font>

223
00:16:07,514 --> 00:16:10,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought I'd go over to his neck of the woods.</b></font>

224
00:16:10,194 --> 00:16:15,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kyoichi's home course is
the Iroha Slope in Nikko.</b></font>

225
00:16:15,834 --> 00:16:19,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To do it there would be to face a
powerful enemy, and no small feat.</b></font>

226
00:16:32,234 --> 00:16:35,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He may not look it, but he quite dislikes losing.</i></b></font>

227
00:16:35,474 --> 00:16:39,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I like his idea of diving</i>
<i>straight into enemy territory...</i></b></font>

228
00:16:39,834 --> 00:16:44,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It is a quality he will certainly</i>
<i>need in order to become faster.</i></b></font>

229
00:16:47,194 --> 00:16:48,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Tochigi Prefecture"</b></font>

230
00:16:52,434 --> 00:16:54,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello, Fujiwara Tofu Shop.</b></font>

231
00:16:54,434 --> 00:16:56,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello! Um, this is Takeuchi...</b></font>

232
00:16:56,994 --> 00:16:59,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. Takumi?</b></font>

233
00:16:59,434 --> 00:17:01,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nah, he's not here.</b></font>

234
00:17:01,154 --> 00:17:04,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's not?! So he went out in the car?</b></font>

235
00:17:04,354 --> 00:17:07,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um, where to?</b></font>

236
00:17:07,194 --> 00:17:10,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know nothin' about that.</b></font>

237
00:17:15,394 --> 00:17:17,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Steep hill roads ahead</b></font>

238
00:17:15,394 --> 00:17:17,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Use engine braking</b></font>

239
00:17:15,394 --> 00:17:17,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Beware of brakes overheating"</b></font>

240
00:17:29,674 --> 00:17:31,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is the Iroha Slope, huh?</i></b></font>

241
00:17:31,914 --> 00:17:34,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Looking at the map, there were</i>
<i>two roads with the same name,</i></b></font>

242
00:17:34,794 --> 00:17:39,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>which was weird, but actually</i>
<i>coming here, I get it now.</i></b></font>

243
00:17:41,914 --> 00:17:46,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There are separate, one-way roads</i>
<i>for going up and coming down...</i></b></font>

244
00:17:46,554 --> 00:17:49,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So there are even roadways like this one, huh?</i></b></font>

245
00:18:05,714 --> 00:18:09,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Still, this downward route is amazing!</i></b></font>

246
00:18:09,114 --> 00:18:11,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Danger"</b></font>

247
00:18:12,714 --> 00:18:15,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>- Hey, that car!
- Yeah!</b></font>

248
00:18:15,554 --> 00:18:17,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? What'd you say?</b></font>

249
00:18:17,394 --> 00:18:19,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>H-Hey, there!</b></font>

250
00:18:22,794 --> 00:18:26,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>- Is that?
- The Eight-Six of Akina!</b></font>

251
00:18:30,834 --> 00:18:32,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Panorama Rest House"</b></font>

252
00:18:31,434 --> 00:18:32,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What was that?!</b></font>

253
00:18:32,954 --> 00:18:33,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What was that?!</b></font>

254
00:18:33,634 --> 00:18:35,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. Understood.</b></font>

255
00:18:35,914 --> 00:18:39,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kyoichi, we've gotten word from down below.</b></font>

256
00:18:39,354 --> 00:18:43,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A car resembling "the one" will
arrive here at the top shortly!</b></font>

257
00:18:47,314 --> 00:18:49,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big brother! Are you here?</b></font>

258
00:18:49,114 --> 00:18:51,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke? What's happened?</b></font>

259
00:18:51,514 --> 00:18:56,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We've gotten word...
Akina's Eight-Six is at Iroha Slope!</b></font>

260
00:18:56,114 --> 00:18:58,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ah. As expected.</b></font>

261
00:18:58,834 --> 00:19:00,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? You knew about this?</b></font>

262
00:19:00,594 --> 00:19:01,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I suppose.</b></font>

263
00:19:01,834 --> 00:19:05,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, I wonder if that guy's
after a revenge race.</b></font>

264
00:19:05,874 --> 00:19:10,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I imagine he is not concerned
with merely winning or losing.</b></font>

265
00:19:10,874 --> 00:19:12,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He probably...</b></font>

266
00:19:12,714 --> 00:19:16,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...went to Iroha Slope with
the intent of testing something.</b></font>

267
00:19:25,834 --> 00:19:27,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's here!</b></font>

268
00:19:36,474 --> 00:19:39,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What's this? The Eight-Six</i>
<i>sounds different from before...</i></b></font>

269
00:19:41,354 --> 00:19:43,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This was some while ago, but...</b></font>

270
00:19:43,274 --> 00:19:46,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I heard that a certain two-bit
repair shop in Shibukawa</b></font>

271
00:19:46,394 --> 00:19:50,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>had received a strange sort of
engine via "unofficial" routes.</b></font>

272
00:19:50,714 --> 00:19:51,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A strange engine?</b></font>

273
00:19:51,754 --> 00:19:54,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>While it no longer exists,
long ago a touring car race</b></font>

274
00:19:54,594 --> 00:19:59,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>called Group A was in full swing.
Do you remember it?</b></font>

275
00:19:59,594 --> 00:20:02,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No way! It's a Group A engine?!</b></font>

276
00:20:02,874 --> 00:20:05,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In all likelihood, that's exactly what it is.</b></font>

277
00:20:05,714 --> 00:20:10,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If it's the TRD engine that was
installed in Group A's AE101s,</b></font>

278
00:20:10,274 --> 00:20:13,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it's not just an NA 1.6-Liter engine,
it's a high-performance unit</b></font>

279
00:20:13,714 --> 00:20:18,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that can go over 11,100 RPMs,
squeezing out 240 horsepower.</b></font>

280
00:20:18,274 --> 00:20:21,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was probably de-tuned for street use</b></font>

281
00:20:21,034 --> 00:20:24,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and placed under the hood
of the Akina Eight-Six.</b></font>

282
00:20:24,434 --> 00:20:28,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But even if it is a racing engine,
there's going to be a limit</b></font>

283
00:20:28,234 --> 00:20:32,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to how much power you can
squeeze out of an NA 1.6-Liter unit.</b></font>

284
00:20:32,754 --> 00:20:34,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Correct.</b></font>

285
00:20:35,754 --> 00:20:37,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You repaired the Eight-Six, eh?</b></font>

286
00:20:37,434 --> 00:20:38,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes.</b></font>

287
00:20:38,594 --> 00:20:42,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you remember what I told you at Akagi?</b></font>

288
00:20:42,234 --> 00:20:47,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"We'll race again when you have a
machine capable of competing with me."</b></font>

289
00:20:47,074 --> 00:20:49,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I believe those were my words.</b></font>

290
00:20:49,714 --> 00:20:52,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This isn't the same car it was before.</b></font>

291
00:20:52,834 --> 00:20:58,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And it's a good car for me.
Will you not race against it?</b></font>

292
00:21:01,434 --> 00:21:05,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fine. For me, this battle
has been left unresolved...</b></font>

293
00:21:05,114 --> 00:21:07,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here I shall finish it!</b></font>

294
00:21:07,154 --> 00:21:10,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What I'm concentrating on isn't horsepower...</b></font>

295
00:21:10,794 --> 00:21:12,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's turning!</b></font>

296
00:21:13,834 --> 00:21:19,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Installing that engine will result
in dramatically improved handling.</b></font>

297
00:21:19,434 --> 00:21:22,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His cornering, which already
boasted exceptional turns...</b></font>

298
00:21:22,074 --> 00:21:25,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...will now be even more polished!</b></font>

299
00:21:25,274 --> 00:21:30,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It may allow for an equal fight
against Kyoichi's misfiring system.</b></font>

300
00:21:39,754 --> 00:21:41,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The race will be a single downhill stretch.</b></font>

301
00:21:41,874 --> 00:21:46,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We descend to the bottom,
where the road crosses three bridges.</b></font>

302
00:21:46,154 --> 00:21:49,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The goal is on the other side of the last bridge.</b></font>

303
00:21:49,434 --> 00:21:53,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You go first, and I'll follow.</b></font>

304
00:21:53,154 --> 00:21:57,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you can make it all the way to the
goal without letting me pass, you win.</b></font>

305
00:21:57,114 --> 00:21:59,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But if I pass you, I win. Sound good?</b></font>

306
00:21:59,994 --> 00:22:03,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that!</b></font>

307
00:22:03,154 --> 00:22:08,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you want to say it's unfair,
that would be an insult toward me.</b></font>

308
00:22:08,554 --> 00:22:11,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't forget, the Iroha Slope
is my home course.</b></font>

309
00:22:11,714 --> 00:22:17,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Without a handicap like that,
this would be no contest.</b></font>

310
00:22:17,474 --> 00:22:20,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If there's anything you want to say,
I'll hear it once we're done.</b></font>

311
00:22:20,554 --> 00:22:22,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's begin!</b></font>

312
00:22:27,834 --> 00:22:29,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The downward route of the Iroha Slope</i></b></font>

313
00:22:29,714 --> 00:22:33,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>is just like a Gymkhana course,</i>
<i>but with steep slopes added.</i></b></font>

314
00:22:33,874 --> 00:22:37,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No one can get the better of Kyoichi here!</i></b></font>

315
00:22:37,594 --> 00:22:40,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He has techniques honed in Gymkhana,</i></b></font>

316
00:22:40,354 --> 00:22:42,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>and he's a genius at low-speed cornering!</i></b></font>

317
00:23:12,754 --> 00:23:15,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I see. He has gotten a little faster, eh?</i></b></font>

318
00:23:15,954 --> 00:23:17,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>An increase in acceleration</i>
<i>particular to mechanical tuning</i></b></font>

319
00:23:17,954 --> 00:23:19,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>and different from that of a turbo.</i></b></font>

320
00:23:19,274 --> 00:23:21,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>However, no matter what</i>
<i>tuning was performed...</i></b></font>

321
00:23:21,554 --> 00:23:23,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...it's still an Eight-Six.</i></b></font>

322
00:23:23,874 --> 00:23:26,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have 350 horsepower!</i></b></font>

323
00:23:37,834 --> 00:23:39,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Curve"</b></font>

324
00:23:57,274 --> 00:24:00,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That is a super high-rotation engine...</i></b></font>

325
00:24:00,514 --> 00:24:03,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Wiseass! Does he think a modification like that</i></b></font>

326
00:24:03,234 --> 00:24:06,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>can compete with my misfiring system?!</i></b></font>

327
00:24:26,314 --> 00:24:29,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No matter what car challenges me,</i>
<i>I cannot lose here!</i></b></font>

328
00:24:29,834 --> 00:24:35,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>As with Ryosuke in Akagi,</i>
<i>here I am the emperor!</i></b></font>

329
00:24:35,314 --> 00:24:37,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I won't let my prey escape!</i></b></font>

330
00:24:45,874 --> 00:24:47,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's staying right on me...</i></b></font>

331
00:24:47,874 --> 00:24:50,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Anyway, all I can do is go all-out!</i></b></font>

332
00:24:54,674 --> 00:24:56,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This slope will soon level out...</i></b></font>

333
00:24:56,994 --> 00:24:59,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Eight-Six will slow down there, too.</i></b></font>

334
00:24:59,234 --> 00:25:03,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There will be absolutely no</i>
<i>escape from my counterattack!</i></b></font>

335
00:25:09,434 --> 00:25:11,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Danger"</b></font>

336
00:25:11,994 --> 00:25:14,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The greatest pitfall of this course</i></b></font>

337
00:25:14,434 --> 00:25:18,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>is not being able to suddenly switch from</i></b></font>

338
00:25:18,074 --> 00:25:21,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>the incredibly long slow section</i>
<i>to the high-speed side!</i></b></font>

339
00:25:21,394 --> 00:25:24,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even the most skilled racers fall into this trap!</i></b></font>

340
00:25:24,394 --> 00:25:28,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This isn't about technique;</i>
<i>it's about instinctual sensitivity!</i></b></font>

341
00:25:28,354 --> 00:25:31,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No one can suddenly switch</i>
<i>and adapt to the high-speed side!</i></b></font>

342
00:25:33,394 --> 00:25:36,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Save for one exception...</i></b></font>

343
00:25:36,354 --> 00:25:39,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The White Comet of Akagi, Ryosuke Takahashi!</i></b></font>

344
00:25:39,794 --> 00:25:41,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Only he...</i></b></font>

345
00:25:55,114 --> 00:25:56,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A bridge?!</i></b></font>

346
00:25:56,714 --> 00:25:58,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Is the goal coming up soon?</i></b></font>

347
00:25:58,634 --> 00:26:02,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The first bridge! This is the end</i>
<i>of the steep-gradient section.</i></b></font>

348
00:26:02,274 --> 00:26:05,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>From here, this will require all-out power.</i></b></font>

349
00:26:05,634 --> 00:26:10,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I will show you...</i>
<i>the Kyoichi Sudou-style winning equation!</i></b></font>

350
00:26:30,074 --> 00:26:31,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The second bridge...</b></font>

351
00:26:31,434 --> 00:26:33,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And a high-speed right corner,</i>
<i>as if one had been</i></b></font>

352
00:26:33,634 --> 00:26:35,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>shot from the top of the</i>
<i>bridge from a catapult.</i></b></font>

353
00:26:35,554 --> 00:26:37,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>For senses accustomed to</i>
<i>the slow-velocity section,</i></b></font>

354
00:26:37,674 --> 00:26:40,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>it's frightening enough</i>
<i>to make your heart leap out!</i></b></font>

355
00:26:40,434 --> 00:26:42,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>An optical illusion, the road seems to close in,</i></b></font>

356
00:26:42,914 --> 00:26:44,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>leaving no room on the outside.</i></b></font>

357
00:26:44,754 --> 00:26:47,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If I just slightly nudge my way in there...</i></b></font>

358
00:26:49,634 --> 00:26:52,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This race is mine!</b></font>

359
00:26:55,994 --> 00:26:57,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The third bridge.</i></b></font>

360
00:26:57,634 --> 00:26:59,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On that bridge, the outside
becomes the inside.</b></font>

361
00:26:59,834 --> 00:27:02,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For me it's the same finish as always!</b></font>

362
00:27:02,794 --> 00:27:05,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The moment I pulled
alongside him, it was all over!</b></font>

363
00:27:07,034 --> 00:27:08,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I see it! Do I go?</i></b></font>

364
00:27:08,874 --> 00:27:10,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Go!</i></b></font>

365
00:27:11,474 --> 00:27:13,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! Idiot! Does he want to die?!</b></font>

366
00:27:13,714 --> 00:27:15,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's going too fast! He can't turn!</b></font>

367
00:27:15,994 --> 00:27:20,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Turn! Come on, turn! My Eight-Six!</b></font>

368
00:27:20,994 --> 00:27:22,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can he make it?!</b></font>

369
00:27:34,034 --> 00:27:35,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In today's race,</b></font>

370
00:27:35,714 --> 00:27:39,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the quick left turn going into
the third bridge was everything.</b></font>

371
00:27:39,994 --> 00:27:42,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A normal Eight-Six couldn't
make that turn there...</b></font>

372
00:27:42,714 --> 00:27:47,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Or rather, a person with normal
nerves wouldn't plow in like that.</b></font>

373
00:27:47,674 --> 00:27:49,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Were you sure of what you were doing?</b></font>

374
00:27:49,714 --> 00:27:52,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I... I start to "see" the road.</b></font>

375
00:27:52,994 --> 00:27:56,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Earlier, too, I could clearly see the line</b></font>

376
00:27:56,234 --> 00:27:59,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that my car's outer tires would be following.</b></font>

377
00:27:59,714 --> 00:28:02,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought I could just barely make it,
so I eased up on the brakes</b></font>

378
00:28:02,354 --> 00:28:04,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and went as-is.</b></font>

379
00:28:04,714 --> 00:28:09,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't really explain it,
but I've always been this way.</b></font>

380
00:28:09,154 --> 00:28:11,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once I've "seen" a road, I can just drive it.</b></font>

381
00:28:11,354 --> 00:28:12,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see...</b></font>

382
00:28:12,994 --> 00:28:15,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a strange car, that one.</b></font>

383
00:28:15,554 --> 00:28:18,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not a car that just anyone
can drive, I'll give you that.</b></font>

384
00:28:18,834 --> 00:28:20,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a good car.</b></font>

385
00:28:20,154 --> 00:28:21,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It is?</b></font>

386
00:28:21,834 --> 00:28:25,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I lost. Let's meet again if we have the chance.</b></font>

387
00:28:29,514 --> 00:28:34,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm really happy, but... I don't feel like I won.</b></font>

388
00:28:34,874 --> 00:28:38,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe it was a draw, if you look at it fairly...</b></font>

389
00:28:44,194 --> 00:28:46,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi! Get up!</b></font>

390
00:28:48,394 --> 00:28:52,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You were out pretty late
last night. Where'd you go?</b></font>

391
00:28:53,274 --> 00:28:54,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iroha Slope.</b></font>

392
00:28:54,874 --> 00:29:00,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Say, Pops, going forward,
there's probably going to be more of this.</b></font>

393
00:29:00,154 --> 00:29:03,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Getting back just in time and
going straight out to deliver...</b></font>

394
00:29:03,274 --> 00:29:05,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think there are going to be times like that.</b></font>

395
00:29:05,434 --> 00:29:09,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If ya make it back in time to deliver,
I've got no complaints.</b></font>

396
00:29:09,474 --> 00:29:11,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>More to the point... Here.</b></font>

397
00:29:13,674 --> 00:29:16,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't want ya dozin' off
and wreckin' the tofu.</b></font>

398
00:29:16,714 --> 00:29:19,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Drive careful so you don't spill the water.</b></font>

399
00:29:19,794 --> 00:29:21,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, yeah, I know.</b></font>

400
00:29:21,314 --> 00:29:23,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right, I'm off.</b></font>

401
00:29:45,354 --> 00:29:47,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke...</b></font>

402
00:29:52,994 --> 00:29:56,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard. You went up against
an Evo III at Iroha Slope.</b></font>

403
00:29:56,834 --> 00:30:00,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You already know about that?</b></font>

404
00:30:00,154 --> 00:30:04,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Those sorts of stories get spread around fast.</b></font>

405
00:30:04,314 --> 00:30:06,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'll be winter soon.</b></font>

406
00:30:06,274 --> 00:30:10,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our expeditionary plan will start in earnest</b></font>

407
00:30:10,634 --> 00:30:15,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>in spring of next year, once the
icy road season has finished.</b></font>

408
00:30:15,194 --> 00:30:20,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're coming, right? With our new team?</b></font>

409
00:30:20,114 --> 00:30:23,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My big brother's time limit is one more year.</b></font>

410
00:30:23,154 --> 00:30:25,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So I want to give everything
I've got during that year</b></font>

411
00:30:25,834 --> 00:30:28,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and race for my big brother's dream.</b></font>

412
00:30:28,794 --> 00:30:32,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In this grand game he's so passionate about...</b></font>

413
00:30:32,714 --> 00:30:35,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...what sort of catharsis will be at the ending?</b></font>

414
00:30:35,634 --> 00:30:40,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to know that! If you let
my big brother teach you,</b></font>

415
00:30:40,154 --> 00:30:43,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>after one year, I'm sure you'll be crazy good.</b></font>

416
00:30:43,874 --> 00:30:48,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I'm gonna get to a level
far above even that.</b></font>

417
00:30:48,674 --> 00:30:53,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our race will wait until then...</b></font>

418
00:30:53,074 --> 00:30:57,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But in one year's time,
I'll beat you and attempt to go pro!</b></font>

419
00:30:57,314 --> 00:31:00,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going to be a big, major-league name.</b></font>

420
00:31:03,194 --> 00:31:05,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come with us.</b></font>

421
00:31:05,434 --> 00:31:07,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's do this, together.</b></font>

422
00:31:18,594 --> 00:31:20,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Incredible...</i></b></font>

423
00:31:20,794 --> 00:31:23,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What incredible people!</i></b></font>

424
00:31:27,394 --> 00:31:29,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? Is that for real?</b></font>

425
00:31:29,794 --> 00:31:33,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's for real! He totally took on
Sudou of Team Emperor</b></font>

426
00:31:33,074 --> 00:31:36,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>for a downhill battle on Iroha Slope!</b></font>

427
00:31:36,634 --> 00:31:37,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And what was the outcome?</b></font>

428
00:31:37,954 --> 00:31:40,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi says it was a draw.</b></font>

429
00:31:40,754 --> 00:31:42,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A draw?</b></font>

430
00:31:42,194 --> 00:31:45,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. But friggin' Takumi,
he looked content with that.</b></font>

431
00:31:45,394 --> 00:31:49,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't doubt it. Sudou's speed is renowned...</b></font>

432
00:31:49,154 --> 00:31:53,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...and what's more, this was
on the enemy's home course.</b></font>

433
00:31:53,074 --> 00:31:56,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That being said, the Eight-Six's new engine</b></font>

434
00:31:56,234 --> 00:32:00,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>may be an absolute devil of a thing.</b></font>

435
00:32:00,714 --> 00:32:03,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi may well have awesome technique,</b></font>

436
00:32:03,394 --> 00:32:06,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but having enough power to
go up against a Lancer Evo...</b></font>

437
00:32:06,914 --> 00:32:09,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think that makes this a serious matter.</b></font>

438
00:32:09,994 --> 00:32:12,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A serious matter?</b></font>

439
00:32:12,154 --> 00:32:16,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. For the first time,
Takumi has acquired a machine</b></font>

440
00:32:16,394 --> 00:32:20,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>at which he can throw
everything he's capable of.</b></font>

441
00:32:20,354 --> 00:32:23,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Perhaps the true legend of
Akina's unbeatable Eight-Six...</b></font>

442
00:32:23,154 --> 00:32:25,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...is only about to begin.</b></font>

443
00:32:27,354 --> 00:32:29,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Welcome!</b></font>

444
00:32:34,434 --> 00:32:37,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>High octane. Uh... 20.</b></font>

445
00:32:37,314 --> 00:32:39,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Putting in 20 liters of high octane!</b></font>

446
00:32:39,754 --> 00:32:41,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, hang on a minute.</b></font>

447
00:32:41,954 --> 00:32:45,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Make that 15.</b></font>

448
00:32:48,594 --> 00:32:51,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you the Eight-Six of Akina?</b></font>

449
00:32:51,194 --> 00:32:54,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I'm not. And you are?</b></font>

450
00:32:54,114 --> 00:32:58,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I came 'cuz I heard you can
meet Akina's Eight-Six here.</b></font>

451
00:32:58,394 --> 00:33:00,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm Kogashiwa.</b></font>

452
00:33:01,674 --> 00:33:05,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Tochigi"</b></font>

453
00:33:02,234 --> 00:33:05,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kogashiwa, he said? It can't be!</i></b></font>

454
00:33:35,154 --> 00:33:36,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here it comes!</b></font>

455
00:33:36,434 --> 00:33:38,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hyaa!</b></font>

456
00:33:38,434 --> 00:33:40,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Aww, jeez!</b></font>

457
00:33:42,514 --> 00:33:45,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>- Hyaa!
- Okay!</b></font>

458
00:33:47,834 --> 00:33:50,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't go there, it's dangerous!</b></font>

459
00:34:30,794 --> 00:34:35,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Order in! Fast Burger, small fries,
and iced tea, no sugar...</b></font>

460
00:34:35,954 --> 00:34:37,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One of each!</b></font>

461
00:34:37,274 --> 00:34:39,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay!</b></font>

462
00:34:44,274 --> 00:34:47,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's not here yet, but he should be by 5:00.</b></font>

463
00:34:47,674 --> 00:34:51,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He said he had somewhere to go...</b></font>

464
00:34:51,234 --> 00:34:53,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay. I'll come by again.</b></font>

465
00:34:53,394 --> 00:34:54,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sir!</b></font>

466
00:34:54,714 --> 00:34:57,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You said "Kogashiwa" just now, didn't you?</b></font>

467
00:34:57,274 --> 00:35:00,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I apologize if I'm mistaken, but...</b></font>

468
00:35:00,354 --> 00:35:03,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Could that be as in Ken Kogashiwa?</b></font>

469
00:35:03,594 --> 00:35:07,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ken Kogashiwa... is my father.</b></font>

470
00:35:07,634 --> 00:35:10,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much!</b></font>

471
00:35:07,634 --> 00:35:10,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Gas"</b></font>

472
00:35:10,474 --> 00:35:10,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much!</b></font>

473
00:35:10,834 --> 00:35:15,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come on manager, please tell me
about that customer just now!</b></font>

474
00:35:15,034 --> 00:35:16,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What was that about?</b></font>

475
00:35:16,274 --> 00:35:18,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You mean about Ken Kogashiwa?</b></font>

476
00:35:18,074 --> 00:35:20,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah! Just who is he?</b></font>

477
00:35:20,954 --> 00:35:23,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'd been a long time since
I'd thought of that name.</b></font>

478
00:35:23,874 --> 00:35:30,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How many years, I wonder...
Twenty years? No, easily more than that.</b></font>

479
00:35:30,754 --> 00:35:35,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Back then, Bunta and I were
running various mountain passes...</b></font>

480
00:35:35,794 --> 00:35:40,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...and Ken Kogashiwa was a
rally racer working the Iroha Slope.</b></font>

481
00:35:40,194 --> 00:35:43,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At the time, he was Bunta's greatest rival.</b></font>

482
00:35:43,674 --> 00:35:47,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, he had a crazy racing style.</b></font>

483
00:35:47,034 --> 00:35:49,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He went up against Bunta several times,</b></font>

484
00:35:49,234 --> 00:35:52,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and in the last big race, Bunta won.</b></font>

485
00:35:52,194 --> 00:35:55,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We didn't hear a single
thing from him after that.</b></font>

486
00:35:55,474 --> 00:35:59,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Bunta Fujiwara, legendary</i>
<i>racer and Takumi's father.</i></b></font>

487
00:35:59,114 --> 00:36:01,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And this is his rival...</i></b></font>

488
00:36:01,394 --> 00:36:07,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His son grew up so fast, and
now he's come to meet Takumi...</b></font>

489
00:36:31,714 --> 00:36:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That was some pretty good driving.</i></b></font>

490
00:36:34,234 --> 00:36:37,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What was that just now?! What happened?</b></font>

491
00:36:37,554 --> 00:36:40,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I felt a jolt just by going past him!</b></font>

492
00:36:40,994 --> 00:36:44,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I still don't get it... But it was awesome!</b></font>

493
00:36:44,234 --> 00:36:46,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A challenge to a race?</b></font>

494
00:36:46,434 --> 00:36:49,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the sort of feel it had to it.</b></font>

495
00:36:49,634 --> 00:36:53,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah! And I think it was an SW20
with a Tochigi license plate.</b></font>

496
00:36:53,714 --> 00:36:57,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That car's a mid-engine, so it
has formidable racing power.</b></font>

497
00:36:57,434 --> 00:36:59,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Mid-engine"?</b></font>

498
00:36:59,274 --> 00:36:59,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Mid-engine"?</b></font>

499
00:36:59,274 --> 00:37:06,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Now accepting card applications!"</b></font>

500
00:36:59,434 --> 00:37:03,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It means the engine is
located behind the driver.</b></font>

501
00:37:03,554 --> 00:37:06,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In normal cars it's in front of the driver's seat,</b></font>

502
00:37:06,754 --> 00:37:06,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In normal cars it's in front of the driver's seat,</b></font>

503
00:37:06,874 --> 00:37:08,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but in a mid-engine, it's opposite.</b></font>

504
00:37:08,874 --> 00:37:12,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In a rear-axle drive,
having the engine to the rear</b></font>

505
00:37:12,314 --> 00:37:15,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>makes the tires less likely to slide
when your foot's on the gas.</b></font>

506
00:37:15,634 --> 00:37:18,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That gives it the acceleration
advantage when coming out of corners.</b></font>

507
00:37:18,794 --> 00:37:21,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Having that heavy engine
centrally located in the car frame</b></font>

508
00:37:21,794 --> 00:37:24,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>has the benefit of increased maneuverability.</b></font>

509
00:37:24,634 --> 00:37:27,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>F-1 machines are all mid-engines, too.</b></font>

510
00:37:29,874 --> 00:37:31,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>H-He's here!</b></font>

511
00:37:35,274 --> 00:37:38,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

512
00:37:35,794 --> 00:37:38,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, Fujiwara Tofu Shop.</b></font>

513
00:37:38,794 --> 00:37:38,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, Fujiwara Tofu Shop.</b></font>

514
00:37:38,954 --> 00:37:44,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kogashiwa? Ken Kogashiwa?
This is unexpected!</b></font>

515
00:37:44,394 --> 00:37:47,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How many years has it been
since I've heard your voice?</b></font>

516
00:37:49,154 --> 00:37:51,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So you're the Akina Eight-Six?</b></font>

517
00:37:51,994 --> 00:37:55,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It seems you beat Sudou of
Team Emperor at Iroha Slope.</b></font>

518
00:37:55,394 --> 00:37:57,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sudou was <i>my</i> target!</b></font>

519
00:37:57,834 --> 00:38:02,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The locals said that loud,
sputtering Evo III was unbeatable...</b></font>

520
00:38:02,834 --> 00:38:05,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I was confident I would defeat it!</b></font>

521
00:38:05,474 --> 00:38:09,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was so close, and you swooped
in and stole all my thunder!</b></font>

522
00:38:09,194 --> 00:38:14,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why my target has shifted
automatically over to you.</b></font>

523
00:38:14,514 --> 00:38:17,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to challenge you!</b></font>

524
00:38:17,314 --> 00:38:19,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well? What's your answer?</b></font>

525
00:38:23,714 --> 00:38:26,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't feel I beat the Evo III,</b></font>

526
00:38:26,514 --> 00:38:30,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but after a story like that,
I don't intend to run away!</b></font>

527
00:38:33,034 --> 00:38:35,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't say when, but before snow falls,</b></font>

528
00:38:35,554 --> 00:38:38,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I will definitely go to Iroha Slope again!</b></font>

529
00:38:38,834 --> 00:38:42,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fine, understood. I look
forward to it with pleasure.</b></font>

530
00:38:42,674 --> 00:38:45,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My name is Kai Kogashiwa. And you are?</b></font>

531
00:38:45,714 --> 00:38:50,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi Fujiwara. Sorry,
but I'm working right now, so...</b></font>

532
00:38:50,194 --> 00:38:54,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ah, my apologies. Oh, and one more thing.</b></font>

533
00:38:54,034 --> 00:38:56,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Were you out racing on Akina earlier?</b></font>

534
00:38:56,554 --> 00:38:57,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No...</b></font>

535
00:38:57,794 --> 00:39:01,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. Then, no matter.</b></font>

536
00:39:21,194 --> 00:39:23,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

537
00:39:26,914 --> 00:39:29,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What're you doing, Pops?</b></font>

538
00:39:30,514 --> 00:39:33,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi...</b></font>

539
00:39:33,874 --> 00:39:37,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Someone came to meet you today, didn't he?</b></font>

540
00:39:37,114 --> 00:39:41,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Driving a squat-looking car called an SW20...</b></font>

541
00:39:41,074 --> 00:39:43,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How did you know that?</b></font>

542
00:39:45,794 --> 00:39:48,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you plan to race him?</b></font>

543
00:39:48,194 --> 00:39:49,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

544
00:39:49,874 --> 00:39:54,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hate running away from a challenge.</b></font>

545
00:39:54,194 --> 00:39:57,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You... would lose.</b></font>

546
00:40:09,754 --> 00:40:14,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Dad, I went to where
Akina's Eight-Six is yesterday.</b></font>

547
00:40:14,234 --> 00:40:19,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that so? You're finally going
to challenge Fujiwara's son?</b></font>

548
00:40:19,474 --> 00:40:21,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know about that, Dad?</b></font>

549
00:40:21,434 --> 00:40:24,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, there's a bit of a backstory there...</b></font>

550
00:40:24,834 --> 00:40:30,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kai, there is a good strategy
for beating the Eight-Six!</b></font>

551
00:40:35,274 --> 00:40:38,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>- See ya!
- Okay, see you tomorrow.</b></font>

552
00:40:40,394 --> 00:40:42,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Takumi!</i></b></font>

553
00:40:44,034 --> 00:40:48,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come on Takumi, don't ignore me.</b></font>

554
00:40:48,034 --> 00:40:51,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to talk to you about
something. Meet me later.</b></font>

555
00:40:51,314 --> 00:40:52,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why tell me?</b></font>

556
00:40:52,834 --> 00:40:55,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're friends, aren't we?</b></font>

557
00:40:55,194 --> 00:40:56,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Friends"?</b></font>

558
00:40:56,714 --> 00:41:01,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, you told me before that
it's not as if we're dating, right?</b></font>

559
00:41:01,674 --> 00:41:04,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>S-So that makes us friends, right?</b></font>

560
00:41:04,354 --> 00:41:08,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And if we're friends, then you can
help me with some advice, right?</b></font>

561
00:41:08,154 --> 00:41:12,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, wait! Meet with me, please!</b></font>

562
00:41:12,594 --> 00:41:15,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I... I'm busy.</b></font>

563
00:41:26,714 --> 00:41:29,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

564
00:41:29,514 --> 00:41:34,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, when are you thinking
about going to Iroha Slope?</b></font>

565
00:41:34,074 --> 00:41:37,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once you decide to do something,
sooner is better, right?</b></font>

566
00:41:37,034 --> 00:41:40,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not as if delaying it will change anything...</b></font>

567
00:41:40,354 --> 00:41:42,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why I'm going tonight.</b></font>

568
00:41:42,674 --> 00:41:44,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're joking, right? Are you serious?!</b></font>

569
00:41:44,914 --> 00:41:46,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I mean it.</b></font>

570
00:41:46,994 --> 00:41:49,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tomorrow's Saturday, so it's
only a half day at school...</b></font>

571
00:41:49,594 --> 00:41:52,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll probably be all right even if
I don't sleep too much tonight.</b></font>

572
00:41:52,594 --> 00:41:56,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When you make up your mind,
you don't mess around, do you?</b></font>

573
00:41:56,754 --> 00:42:00,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, what are you gonna do?
About the new team.</b></font>

574
00:42:00,874 --> 00:42:02,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

575
00:42:02,154 --> 00:42:04,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're joining, right?
Have you already told them?</b></font>

576
00:42:04,514 --> 00:42:05,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not yet.</b></font>

577
00:42:05,914 --> 00:42:07,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not yet?!</b></font>

578
00:42:07,754 --> 00:42:12,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It looks like the team's not going
to really get moving till spring.</b></font>

579
00:42:12,994 --> 00:42:15,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've got a bit of time till then.</b></font>

580
00:42:15,994 --> 00:42:18,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's a lot for me to think about.</b></font>

581
00:42:18,754 --> 00:42:20,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Think about?</b></font>

582
00:42:20,194 --> 00:42:24,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My heart's in it, but it's just so intimidating.</b></font>

583
00:42:24,394 --> 00:42:27,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke and Keisuke are incredible people.</b></font>

584
00:42:27,394 --> 00:42:33,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They have such firm senses of purpose...</b></font>

585
00:42:33,274 --> 00:42:38,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Me, I just sort of want to go fast, that's it.</b></font>

586
00:42:38,874 --> 00:42:41,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A sense of purpose, huh?</b></font>

587
00:42:49,594 --> 00:42:51,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You going?</b></font>

588
00:42:51,594 --> 00:42:52,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

589
00:42:52,914 --> 00:42:56,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Aah. It's pretty tough over there.</b></font>

590
00:42:56,234 --> 00:42:58,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll give you one piece of advice.</b></font>

591
00:42:58,274 --> 00:43:00,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? This is unexpected!</b></font>

592
00:43:00,714 --> 00:43:03,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just shut up and listen.</b></font>

593
00:43:05,994 --> 00:43:08,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm only gonna say this once.</b></font>

594
00:43:08,074 --> 00:43:12,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can trap him at the area
of the last bridge. By then...</b></font>

595
00:43:12,074 --> 00:43:14,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...he's sure to be in front of you.</b></font>

596
00:43:14,674 --> 00:43:17,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can't know that, can you?!</b></font>

597
00:43:25,674 --> 00:43:27,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good!</b></font>

598
00:43:31,834 --> 00:43:35,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Listen here, Kai.
You're up against Fujiwara's son.</b></font>

599
00:43:35,594 --> 00:43:38,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's bound to be incredibly skilled.</b></font>

600
00:43:38,354 --> 00:43:43,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Winning this race will require
both strategy and technique.</b></font>

601
00:43:43,114 --> 00:43:47,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I will tell you the strategy
for beating Fujiwara's son.</b></font>

602
00:43:47,354 --> 00:43:51,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>First, let him get ahead of you.</b></font>

603
00:43:51,154 --> 00:43:55,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you nuts?! That idiot
"strategy" can go screw itself!</b></font>

604
00:43:55,514 --> 00:43:58,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you let someone who may
be faster go in front of you,</b></font>

605
00:43:58,794 --> 00:44:01,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>then of course you're gonna lose!</b></font>

606
00:44:01,634 --> 00:44:05,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Think clearly, and you'll see that
overtaking him is just impossible!</b></font>

607
00:44:05,714 --> 00:44:09,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To be sure, a standard
approach would be of no use...</b></font>

608
00:44:09,794 --> 00:44:13,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That is exactly what makes this a strategy!</b></font>

609
00:44:13,074 --> 00:44:15,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At the Iroha Slope, sometimes a line appears</b></font>

610
00:44:15,274 --> 00:44:18,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that is even farther in than the corner line.</b></font>

611
00:44:18,714 --> 00:44:20,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're telling me I should follow it?!</b></font>

612
00:44:20,794 --> 00:44:23,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're okay with that, Dad? Whatever
happens to the car ain't my fault!</b></font>

613
00:44:23,954 --> 00:44:28,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just do it. Then, overtaking him
will be, to use a boxing metaphor,</b></font>

614
00:44:28,354 --> 00:44:30,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>a win by knockout!</b></font>

615
00:44:30,234 --> 00:44:36,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This time, make sure anyone who
sees will know it's a clear win!</b></font>

616
00:44:36,834 --> 00:44:40,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Listen Kai, set him up after the midway point.</b></font>

617
00:44:40,554 --> 00:44:43,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Till then, whatever else, just keep up with him.</b></font>

618
00:44:44,354 --> 00:44:45,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Tochigi Prefecture"</b></font>

619
00:44:51,874 --> 00:44:56,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Under his dad's gifted tutelage,
he started doing karts as a kid,</b></font>

620
00:44:56,154 --> 00:44:59,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>winning who knows how many races.</b></font>

621
00:44:59,874 --> 00:45:03,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's a legit racer like
that doing on the streets?</b></font>

622
00:45:03,394 --> 00:45:05,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who knows? Before that,
he'd apparently been the fastest</b></font>

623
00:45:05,914 --> 00:45:08,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to do the Iroha Slope on a motorcycle.</b></font>

624
00:45:08,234 --> 00:45:12,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, that's right. There's an
Emperor named Seiji lwaki, right?</b></font>

625
00:45:12,514 --> 00:45:14,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He rode a white Evo IV...</b></font>

626
00:45:14,714 --> 00:45:18,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, that bastard who had his
hair done up in back, right?</b></font>

627
00:45:18,874 --> 00:45:21,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When Team Emperor invaded the Gunma area,</b></font>

628
00:45:21,674 --> 00:45:24,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he beat everyone single-handed, right?</b></font>

629
00:45:24,314 --> 00:45:27,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It seems that same lwaki was
recently rather soundly beaten</b></font>

630
00:45:27,194 --> 00:45:29,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>by that SW.</b></font>

631
00:45:41,474 --> 00:45:43,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You again?!</b></font>

632
00:45:43,594 --> 00:45:47,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have no intention of going up
against you all tonight, lwaki.</b></font>

633
00:45:47,914 --> 00:45:51,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just thought I'd give you a brief heads-up.</b></font>

634
00:45:51,234 --> 00:45:52,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A heads-up?</b></font>

635
00:45:52,874 --> 00:45:55,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tonight, I'll be racing the
Eight-Six of Akina here.</b></font>

636
00:45:55,554 --> 00:45:56,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

637
00:45:56,554 --> 00:46:00,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It won't do for you to
keep losing to outsiders...</b></font>

638
00:46:00,114 --> 00:46:02,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So I'll put a stop to him, Sudou.</b></font>

639
00:46:02,514 --> 00:46:05,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>- Bastard!
- It's an interesting match, don't you think?</b></font>

640
00:46:05,954 --> 00:46:09,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Akina's Eight-Six vs. Kogashiwa,
graduate of kart racing.</b></font>

641
00:46:09,794 --> 00:46:13,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What shall be the result?
I'm quite eager to know.</b></font>

642
00:46:22,434 --> 00:46:26,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thanks for coming. Do you not
need to take a look at the course?</b></font>

643
00:46:26,034 --> 00:46:30,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I already have. I got here early, so I did a lap.</b></font>

644
00:46:30,594 --> 00:46:34,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then I will explain the rules.
We start at the same time.</b></font>

645
00:46:34,514 --> 00:46:37,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When you've completely crossed the
third bridge, you've crossed the goal line.</b></font>

646
00:46:37,354 --> 00:46:40,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whoever gets there first wins.</b></font>

647
00:46:40,714 --> 00:46:42,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You good with that?</b></font>

648
00:46:42,834 --> 00:46:44,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then let's begin.</b></font>

649
00:46:48,314 --> 00:46:49,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's no mistake...</i></b></font>

650
00:46:49,594 --> 00:46:54,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This Eight-Six is the Panda Trueno</i>
<i>I passed in Akina before.</i></b></font>

651
00:46:54,034 --> 00:46:57,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Meaning that the person</i>
<i>behind the wheel then...</i></b></font>

652
00:46:57,994 --> 00:47:04,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...was the guy who beat my dad,</i>
<i>Bunta Fujiwara. And this is his son.</i></b></font>

653
00:47:04,514 --> 00:47:07,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I didn't really "get" it when I
met him at the gas station...</i></b></font>

654
00:47:07,314 --> 00:47:09,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...but now I feel it.</i></b></font>

655
00:47:11,154 --> 00:47:13,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This guy is fast!</i></b></font>

656
00:47:13,234 --> 00:47:16,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What a thrill this has become... I have to do it!</i></b></font>

657
00:47:20,314 --> 00:47:23,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay. Understood.</b></font>

658
00:47:23,034 --> 00:47:24,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It looks like it'll start soon.</b></font>

659
00:47:24,714 --> 00:47:26,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Understood.</b></font>

660
00:47:35,434 --> 00:47:37,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke...</b></font>

661
00:47:38,234 --> 00:47:43,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard there's an interesting
race to be seen here, so I came.</b></font>

662
00:47:44,554 --> 00:47:47,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do as you like.</b></font>

663
00:47:47,034 --> 00:47:50,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The wind is strong tonight...</b></font>

664
00:47:54,514 --> 00:47:57,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It may be dangerous.</b></font>

665
00:47:57,274 --> 00:48:02,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Great piles of dried leaves
are sure to be on the streets.</b></font>

666
00:48:02,434 --> 00:48:07,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At the critical moment,
what decides this competition...</b></font>

667
00:48:07,034 --> 00:48:10,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...may, of all things, be these leaves.</b></font>

668
00:48:10,114 --> 00:48:13,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The whimsy of a fallen leaf, eh?</b></font>

669
00:48:22,114 --> 00:48:24,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi! What do you think?</b></font>

670
00:48:24,234 --> 00:48:26,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please don't get your hopes up too high.</b></font>

671
00:48:26,914 --> 00:48:30,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't have a plan?
Didn't your father say anything?</b></font>

672
00:48:30,274 --> 00:48:36,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, he did, but... It was just nonsense.</b></font>

673
00:48:36,714 --> 00:48:40,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, give me a break!</b></font>

674
00:48:40,274 --> 00:48:43,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The only thing to do is go all-out!</b></font>

675
00:48:43,314 --> 00:48:47,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do your best, Takumi!
You can whup him, I'm sure of it!</b></font>

676
00:48:50,234 --> 00:48:52,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, here goes!</b></font>

677
00:48:54,154 --> 00:48:57,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five... Four... Three...</b></font>

678
00:48:57,394 --> 00:48:59,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Two... One...</b></font>

679
00:48:59,314 --> 00:49:00,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

680
00:49:03,514 --> 00:49:06,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whoa, awesome! The Eight-Six really took off!</b></font>

681
00:49:06,194 --> 00:49:08,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi's so fast!</b></font>

682
00:49:08,674 --> 00:49:12,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Incredible! The mid-engine should have</i>
<i>the advantage at the starting dash...</i></b></font>

683
00:49:12,474 --> 00:49:16,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Eight-Six's new engine</i>
<i>is incredible after all!</i></b></font>

684
00:49:26,154 --> 00:49:29,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's so fast! This is no ordinary Eight-Six.</i></b></font>

685
00:49:29,674 --> 00:49:32,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It has more power than a 2-liter 3S!</i></b></font>

686
00:49:32,794 --> 00:49:35,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My dad said that letting him go ahead</i></b></font>

687
00:49:35,034 --> 00:49:37,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>and then overtaking him</i>
<i>would be a knockout victory.</i></b></font>

688
00:49:37,394 --> 00:49:40,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Good! That's fine by me, too.</i></b></font>

689
00:49:40,994 --> 00:49:43,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll overtake that "fast" Eight-Six</i>
<i>from behind and show them all!</i></b></font>

690
00:49:43,634 --> 00:49:44,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll overtake that "fast" Eight-Six</i>
<i>from behind and show them all!</i></b></font>

691
00:49:43,634 --> 00:49:44,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Reduce Speed"</b></font>

692
00:49:44,474 --> 00:49:44,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll overtake that "fast" Eight-Six</i>
<i>from behind and show them all!</i></b></font>

693
00:49:51,674 --> 00:49:54,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, understood.</b></font>

694
00:49:54,634 --> 00:49:57,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six has been in front since the start.</b></font>

695
00:49:57,354 --> 00:50:00,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That Kogashiwa dude is nothing but talk, huh?</b></font>

696
00:50:00,874 --> 00:50:03,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even <i>you</i> couldn't capture the Eight-Six.</b></font>

697
00:50:03,794 --> 00:50:07,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he let it go first,
his non-turbo SW has no chance!</b></font>

698
00:50:07,874 --> 00:50:09,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know about that.</b></font>

699
00:50:11,074 --> 00:50:16,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I had absolute faith in my counter
strategy just before the goal...</b></font>

700
00:50:16,354 --> 00:50:18,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In that respect, I can't say
that I didn't let my guard down.</b></font>

701
00:50:18,994 --> 00:50:20,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So?</b></font>

702
00:50:20,714 --> 00:50:23,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I avoided unseemly tactics,</b></font>

703
00:50:23,154 --> 00:50:26,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and tried to run a clean
race with no funny business.</b></font>

704
00:50:26,234 --> 00:50:28,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That pride is what dug my grave.</b></font>

705
00:50:28,674 --> 00:50:33,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If Kogashiwa runs an all-out dirty race,
he has a chance at victory.</b></font>

706
00:50:33,554 --> 00:50:35,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you talking about?</b></font>

707
00:50:35,154 --> 00:50:37,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Put simply, a line. There is a special line</b></font>

708
00:50:37,594 --> 00:50:41,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>for overtaking a car that's ahead of you,</b></font>

709
00:50:41,074 --> 00:50:44,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>right here on the Iroha Slope!</b></font>

710
00:50:56,634 --> 00:50:59,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kogashiwa used to race karts,
so he'll use a left-footed brake.</b></font>

711
00:50:59,914 --> 00:51:03,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With his right foot still on the gas,
putting his left on the brake</b></font>

712
00:51:03,114 --> 00:51:06,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>will shift load to the front,
eliminating understeer.</b></font>

713
00:51:06,714 --> 00:51:10,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This way, he can go forward at full throttle!</b></font>

714
00:51:14,434 --> 00:51:16,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On a unique pass like this,</b></font>

715
00:51:16,594 --> 00:51:20,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>there's bound to be things only
a local would know about, huh?</b></font>

716
00:51:20,234 --> 00:51:24,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think Kogashiwa has been
considering various strategies...</b></font>

717
00:51:24,114 --> 00:51:25,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi has the disadvantage.</b></font>

718
00:51:25,794 --> 00:51:30,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But long ago, Takumi's dad raced
Kogashiwa's here and won, right?</b></font>

719
00:51:30,314 --> 00:51:36,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. I thought he'd give some
advice based on the experience...</b></font>

720
00:51:36,314 --> 00:51:39,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but Takumi just showed up half-cocked.</b></font>

721
00:51:39,554 --> 00:51:42,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That Takumi... He's in trouble.</b></font>

722
00:51:49,514 --> 00:51:52,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There are a lot of leaves out tonight...</i></b></font>

723
00:51:52,074 --> 00:51:54,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What's more, the wind</i>
<i>has blown them into piles.</i></b></font>

724
00:51:54,834 --> 00:51:56,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Going over one of those</i>
<i>would send you flying...</i></b></font>

725
00:51:56,794 --> 00:51:58,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This will be difficult.</i></b></font>

726
00:51:58,474 --> 00:52:02,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Still, these conditions should be</i>
<i>harder for the Eight-Six up ahead.</i></b></font>

727
00:52:02,514 --> 00:52:05,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He doesn't know where</i>
<i>or when he's going to slide.</i></b></font>

728
00:52:09,714 --> 00:52:11,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is hard to race!</i></b></font>

729
00:52:11,434 --> 00:52:15,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Instead of just sliding,</i>
<i>maybe I should make it slide.</i></b></font>

730
00:52:15,514 --> 00:52:20,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I should hurry and spin the rear</i>
<i>tires out, and drift all four of them!</i></b></font>

731
00:52:20,834 --> 00:52:22,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's he doing?!</b></font>

732
00:52:22,634 --> 00:52:24,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He plowed right into the pile!</i></b></font>

733
00:52:24,234 --> 00:52:27,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Drifting on a road surface</i>
<i>made easy to slide on, eh?</i></b></font>

734
00:52:30,074 --> 00:52:32,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You're something else, Takumi Fujiwara.</i></b></font>

735
00:52:32,474 --> 00:52:35,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Half-assed tricks won't work on you.</i></b></font>

736
00:52:35,194 --> 00:52:37,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>During the hairpins at the Iroha Slope,
sometimes a line appears</b></font>

737
00:52:37,834 --> 00:52:41,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that is even farther in than the corner line.</b></font>

