<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...that's how intense of an impression I got.</b></font>

882
01:03:13,034 --> 01:03:18,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And I ended up losing, so I guess
my impression was on the mark.</b></font>

883
01:03:18,314 --> 01:03:20,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was a shock to lose on my home turf,</b></font>

884
01:03:20,554 --> 01:03:22,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but that was a good experience you gave me.</b></font>

885
01:03:22,434 --> 01:03:26,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You and your dad are both incredible.</b></font>

886
01:03:26,034 --> 01:03:29,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's do this again somewhere.
I'll sharpen my skills first...</b></font>

887
01:03:29,314 --> 01:03:31,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See you.</b></font>

888
01:03:54,154 --> 01:03:58,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sure is cold today! Takumi,
you got any pocket warmers?!</b></font>

889
01:03:58,994 --> 01:04:00,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hell no, I don't!</b></font>

890
01:04:00,874 --> 01:04:05,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The cold sure sucks, huh?
That harsh wind blowing...</b></font>

891
01:04:07,434 --> 01:04:11,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, what do you think
you'll do after graduation?</b></font>

892
01:04:11,314 --> 01:04:13,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Graduation, huh?</b></font>

893
01:04:13,354 --> 01:04:17,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah! You don't plan on
going to college, right?</b></font>

894
01:04:17,194 --> 01:04:19,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>- I guess not...
- So you goin' to vocational school?</b></font>

895
01:04:19,754 --> 01:04:21,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Uh...</b></font>

896
01:04:21,714 --> 01:04:26,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you haven't made any plans yet,
why not work here with me?</b></font>

897
01:04:26,714 --> 01:04:29,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here?</b></font>

898
01:04:29,114 --> 01:04:32,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm thinking of asking the manager</b></font>

899
01:04:32,194 --> 01:04:35,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to make me a full-time
employee here come April.</b></font>

900
01:04:35,434 --> 01:04:39,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You should do that, too.</b></font>

901
01:04:39,034 --> 01:04:42,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>While you're spacin' out,
more and more time will slip on by!</b></font>

902
01:04:46,274 --> 01:04:48,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See you!</b></font>

903
01:04:58,474 --> 01:05:01,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Isn't it a little different from before? Your car.</b></font>

904
01:05:01,154 --> 01:05:05,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your seat's different, and how
it runs feels different, too.</b></font>

905
01:05:07,794 --> 01:05:11,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Say, Takumi, what are you doing for Christmas?</b></font>

906
01:05:11,634 --> 01:05:13,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nothing really.</b></font>

907
01:05:13,554 --> 01:05:17,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you have a party or
something at your house and stuff?</b></font>

908
01:05:17,034 --> 01:05:21,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since I was a kid, we've never
done anything special for Christmas.</b></font>

909
01:05:21,474 --> 01:05:25,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not like we've got a mom at home, so...</b></font>

910
01:05:25,834 --> 01:05:30,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, enough about that.
What did you want to talk to me about?</b></font>

911
01:05:30,594 --> 01:05:34,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I... I broke up with the guy in the Benz.</b></font>

912
01:05:34,754 --> 01:05:37,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>H-Hey, I don't care about that!</b></font>

913
01:05:37,474 --> 01:05:39,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're lying.</b></font>

914
01:05:39,234 --> 01:05:43,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you really didn't care,
you wouldn't be ignoring me!</b></font>

915
01:05:43,754 --> 01:05:47,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're ignoring me because
you've got me on your mind, right?!</b></font>

916
01:05:47,754 --> 01:05:51,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In the summer, you and I went
to the beach... We even kissed.</b></font>

917
01:05:51,674 --> 01:05:56,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're mad because you feel
like you've been betrayed, right?</b></font>

918
01:05:56,074 --> 01:05:58,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry.</b></font>

919
01:06:10,034 --> 01:06:13,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's cold... It's already winter, huh?</b></font>

920
01:06:13,874 --> 01:06:18,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I... I want us to be close, like we were before.</b></font>

921
01:06:18,474 --> 01:06:21,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't!</b></font>

922
01:06:21,394 --> 01:06:24,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't just switch my way of thinking like that!</b></font>

923
01:06:27,554 --> 01:06:30,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't accept that!</b></font>

924
01:06:32,994 --> 01:06:37,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I won't give up! I'll make up with you for sure!</b></font>

925
01:06:46,194 --> 01:06:48,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's one thing I want to ask you.</b></font>

926
01:06:51,434 --> 01:06:57,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're pretty popular. You could
find plenty of guys to go with, right?</b></font>

927
01:06:57,594 --> 01:07:01,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This isn't like you. Why choose me?!</b></font>

928
01:07:05,354 --> 01:07:08,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Why?" There's no reason...</b></font>

929
01:07:11,834 --> 01:07:15,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Because I like you of course, why else?!</b></font>

930
01:07:45,754 --> 01:07:48,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much!</b></font>

931
01:07:49,554 --> 01:07:51,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani!</b></font>

932
01:07:51,434 --> 01:07:54,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This weather feels like it's gonna
start snowing or something, huh?</b></font>

933
01:07:54,914 --> 01:07:57,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It certainly is cold today.</b></font>

934
01:07:57,434 --> 01:08:00,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>More importantly, Itsuki,
what are you doing for Christmas?</b></font>

935
01:08:00,314 --> 01:08:04,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What am I doing? It's obvious, isn't it?!</b></font>

936
01:08:04,474 --> 01:08:06,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As I thought, a party with your friends?</b></font>

937
01:08:06,674 --> 01:08:09,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, this is your last
Christmas in high school...</b></font>

938
01:08:09,394 --> 01:08:12,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Incorrect! I am working, sir, working!</b></font>

939
01:08:12,474 --> 01:08:14,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have to trade out the
Levin tires on my beloved car</b></font>

940
01:08:14,914 --> 01:08:19,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>with winter-use studless ones!</b></font>

941
01:08:19,674 --> 01:08:24,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just like me at your age.
And what about Takumi?</b></font>

942
01:08:24,994 --> 01:08:26,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Uh, Takumi...</b></font>

943
01:08:28,794 --> 01:08:31,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Man, he can really space out, huh?</b></font>

944
01:08:31,514 --> 01:08:34,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Especially so today...</b></font>

945
01:08:37,434 --> 01:08:43,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

946
01:08:46,434 --> 01:08:49,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey Pops, I...</b></font>

947
01:08:50,954 --> 01:08:54,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um, I'm gonna be graduating soon, right? So...</b></font>

948
01:08:54,994 --> 01:08:57,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just do what you wanna do.</b></font>

949
01:08:58,874 --> 01:09:04,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Tofu"</b></font>

950
01:08:58,874 --> 01:09:04,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fried Tofu"</b></font>

951
01:08:59,354 --> 01:09:03,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whether that's being a tofu man or whatever...</b></font>

952
01:09:22,234 --> 01:09:26,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There are guys with time on their
hands even on Christmas Eve, huh?</b></font>

953
01:09:26,154 --> 01:09:29,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you have somewhere else you can go?</b></font>

954
01:09:29,074 --> 01:09:30,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Man, when you say it like that...</b></font>

955
01:09:30,994 --> 01:09:32,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, who cares?</b></font>

956
01:09:32,794 --> 01:09:35,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter where you go today,
it'll still be rough being alone.</b></font>

957
01:09:35,554 --> 01:09:40,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Look to your right, swing over to
your left, it's nothing but couples!</b></font>

958
01:09:40,434 --> 01:09:44,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On a day like this, we should
go out and eat some great food.</b></font>

959
01:09:44,514 --> 01:09:47,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That sounds good! What about you guys?</b></font>

960
01:09:47,674 --> 01:09:50,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going, of course! I've got nothing to do!</b></font>

961
01:09:50,994 --> 01:09:52,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What about you, Takumi?</b></font>

962
01:09:52,154 --> 01:09:55,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't have any money, so I'm not going.</b></font>

963
01:09:56,394 --> 01:10:00,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the heck?!
You're as unsociable as always!</b></font>

964
01:10:03,874 --> 01:10:05,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Cake Shop"</b></font>

965
01:10:12,354 --> 01:10:17,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tofu shop... Tofu... There it is! I finally found it!</b></font>

966
01:10:19,914 --> 01:10:22,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, here goes!</b></font>

967
01:10:22,194 --> 01:10:26,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure has gotten cold...</b></font>

968
01:10:26,034 --> 01:10:29,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At this rate, there'll be
snow up on the mountain...</b></font>

969
01:10:29,914 --> 01:10:32,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>U-U-Um, tofu... No, not tofu!</b></font>

970
01:10:32,394 --> 01:10:36,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I-I'm a friend of Takumi's.</b></font>

971
01:10:36,434 --> 01:10:40,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ah. He ain't come back from work yet.</b></font>

972
01:10:42,634 --> 01:10:45,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh. Um...</b></font>

973
01:10:47,114 --> 01:10:52,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ah! No, nothing. Sorry to have bothered you.</b></font>

974
01:11:01,674 --> 01:11:05,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Actin' like some middle-aged peddler...</b></font>

975
01:11:07,314 --> 01:11:11,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, you there. That looks heavy and all,</b></font>

976
01:11:11,074 --> 01:11:13,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so if you came to see
my son about something,</b></font>

977
01:11:13,154 --> 01:11:17,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think he'll be back soon,
so come in and have a cup of tea.</b></font>

978
01:11:17,634 --> 01:11:19,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that all right?</b></font>

979
01:11:24,794 --> 01:11:28,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a pain. Stupid Christmas...</b></font>

980
01:11:30,194 --> 01:11:32,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tea's all I've got, but...</b></font>

981
01:11:32,594 --> 01:11:36,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh! So that's what that big thing was!</b></font>

982
01:11:36,274 --> 01:11:41,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's cute, isn't it? Look, the tree even has this...</b></font>

983
01:11:41,314 --> 01:11:43,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's pretty.</b></font>

984
01:11:44,554 --> 01:11:45,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An Eight-Six?</b></font>

985
01:11:45,994 --> 01:11:49,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's handmade. I made it.</b></font>

986
01:11:49,034 --> 01:11:53,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi seems to really like that car, so...</b></font>

987
01:11:53,434 --> 01:11:56,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Friggin' Takumi sure is late.
Where's he wanderin' around at?</b></font>

988
01:11:56,834 --> 01:11:58,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What time were you supposed to meet?</b></font>

989
01:11:58,674 --> 01:12:02,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, uh, we didn't make any arrangements.</b></font>

990
01:12:02,514 --> 01:12:05,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is an unannounced,
"gatecrash" Christmas party.</b></font>

991
01:12:09,114 --> 01:12:11,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>- This, please.
- Yes, sir.</b></font>

992
01:12:20,194 --> 01:12:21,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This hit me a minute ago...</b></font>

993
01:12:21,914 --> 01:12:24,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're the girl who used to call
now and then last summer, right?</b></font>

994
01:12:24,834 --> 01:12:26,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes...</b></font>

995
01:12:26,834 --> 01:12:32,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When those calls suddenly stopped,
I wondered what was up...</b></font>

996
01:12:32,234 --> 01:12:37,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A lot happened... It looked
like Takumi started hating me.</b></font>

997
01:12:37,674 --> 01:12:40,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't want us to graduate
with things like this.</b></font>

998
01:12:40,714 --> 01:12:45,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been trying hard,
but Takumi just won't forgive me...</b></font>

999
01:12:45,754 --> 01:12:50,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know the particulars,
but Takumi ain't one to strut around</b></font>

1000
01:12:50,554 --> 01:12:53,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>choosin' who or who not to forgive.</b></font>

1001
01:12:53,874 --> 01:12:58,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think he probably doesn't really hate ya.</b></font>

1002
01:12:58,354 --> 01:13:02,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He may be just a kid, but he's as stubborn
as an old man about some things.</b></font>

1003
01:13:02,634 --> 01:13:06,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once his mind is set, he totally
refuses to compromise about it.</b></font>

1004
01:13:06,634 --> 01:13:08,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's more, at times like that,</b></font>

1005
01:13:08,674 --> 01:13:12,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>his attitude can be exactly the
opposite of what he really thinks.</b></font>

1006
01:13:14,714 --> 01:13:23,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

1007
01:13:23,714 --> 01:13:25,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm home.</b></font>

1008
01:13:28,154 --> 01:13:31,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? Is someone here?</b></font>

1009
01:13:34,634 --> 01:13:36,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Merry Christmas!</b></font>

1010
01:13:36,594 --> 01:13:38,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the heck is this?</b></font>

1011
01:13:38,274 --> 01:13:40,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Merry Christmas...</b></font>

1012
01:13:40,074 --> 01:13:43,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Pops, you too? What are you doing?!</b></font>

1013
01:13:43,634 --> 01:13:43,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Pops, you too? What are you doing?!</b></font>

1014
01:13:43,634 --> 01:13:46,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Karaoke Club"</b></font>

1015
01:13:43,954 --> 01:13:46,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Merry Christmas!!</b></font>

1016
01:13:46,834 --> 01:13:46,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Merry Christmas!!</b></font>

1017
01:13:46,914 --> 01:13:49,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This sure is fun, huh?!</b></font>

1018
01:13:49,594 --> 01:13:51,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What're we doin' next?</b></font>

1019
01:13:51,594 --> 01:13:54,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not as if he's got any alcohol in him...</b></font>

1020
01:13:54,994 --> 01:13:56,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure is lonely, huh?</b></font>

1021
01:13:56,674 --> 01:13:58,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure is pathetic!</b></font>

1022
01:13:58,074 --> 01:14:00,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>- Mako...
- Huh?</b></font>

1023
01:14:00,114 --> 01:14:04,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Racers don't need women after all, do we?!</b></font>

1024
01:14:06,794 --> 01:14:09,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, put the tree over there.</b></font>

1025
01:14:09,034 --> 01:14:10,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>O-Okay.</b></font>

1026
01:14:10,594 --> 01:14:14,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've loved Christmas
ever since I was a little kid.</b></font>

1027
01:14:14,514 --> 01:14:18,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why I wanted to spend
Christmas with you, Takumi.</b></font>

1028
01:14:18,914 --> 01:14:23,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You said before, right?
You'd never had a Christmas before...</b></font>

1029
01:14:27,434 --> 01:14:32,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, let's eat some cake! Cake! Ta-daa!</b></font>

1030
01:14:32,154 --> 01:14:34,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>- Light the candles!
- Pops, a lighter.</b></font>

